The DA’s federal executive has decided to formally charge and investigate Cape Town Mayor Patricia de Lille.This comes following months of serious claims and counterclaims, involving allegations of intimidation, criminality and misconduct, being exchanged between some of the City of Cape Town’s most senior staff, including De Lille.On Sunday the DA's federal executive met to discuss reasons she submitted detailing why she should not resign as mayor.if(typeof za24_DisplayAd != "undefined") za24_DisplayAd("300x250","2");var viewReq = new Array();function vu(u) {var i=new Image();i.src=u.replace("&amp;","&");viewReq.push(i);}vu("https://securepubads.g.doubleclick.net/pcs/view?xai\x3dAKAOjstROUKwWejnnVUcQmow0PBJlMSwG4RVwZUzEBIRhkcfLRyP__QbzFRwqcKjGhmRKz-E2GkBOVXwF3-Wu6yiz9DuTGEzQx_ANKxMGDuId9wxfUrq0k1e5L5p5t2MgKx3t_rOzqMbzefm7gwo874vaF3pwWWlW8BdMGhg1pMEx4JY7fnWpZnVJbjMFVsCjaaPzY-_RYLKptJ28J-hN1LvTIXkg02YbnJOwmG3yor1zsmUdHBbHhKv2ACeZzDDDPC1dyVvrJvCMCpM7qHMKjJ92gg-iGFGv7w\x26sig\x3dCg0ArKJSzFnOHYYUK5tbEAE\x26urlfix\x3d1\x26adurl\x3d")

   
